  <description><![CDATA[<p>Chalet Hotel Pepi Gabl ticks all the boxes for families wishing to enjoy all that St Anton and the Arlberg ski area has to offer. The location is unrivalled and you'll be based at the peaceful end of the village in the Nasserein area, literally right next door to the gondola and ski school. The ski school can look after your kids all day, giving them plenty of time to learn and make friends – and giving you plenty of time on the slopes. </p>
<p class="js-read-more__parent">The chalet has recently been improved the by the addition of a wonderful family-friendly extension of the communal areas on the ground floor, classic Austrian wooden furnishings feature throughout the building whilst the generous modern lounge provides an ideal area for you to mingle before or after dinner. You'll find a typical Austrian style "stube" dining area with a series of tables with upholstered bench seating, pine-clad walls and decorative ceiling panels. There is also a sep<span>arate adjoining breakfast room to make the start of each day run more smoothly for you. To complete the attraction of the Pepi Gabl, a spacious Wellness area is on the lower ground floor for adults, and an in-house kid’s playrooms (unsupervised) will keep the kids amused.</span></p>
<p>You'll have a choice of bedrooms sleeping up to four as well as a number of family suites with two or three separate sleeping areas, sleeping up to 5 people. </p>]]></description>
